        <abstract>
            <p>Explains what he means when he attempts a "natural classification", defining his words and using man as a standard; gives examples. Classification of Aptera and Diptera.</p>
            <p>Discusses his discharge from the Zoological Society. Is to see Robert Brown about the British Museum position.</p>
